    <p>Our cost-efficient water treatment additives will not only reduce solids in your wastewater but will improve your overall operational efficiency by enabling faster and more efficient material recovery. Some other benefits of our solutions include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Cost-efficiency</li>
      <li>Energy efficiency</li>
      <li>Maximizing the efficiency of water reclamation, recycling, and re-use</li>
