    <p><strong>JAS Global Industries’</strong> UltraFloc® flocculants and coagulants are formulated using various charges, physical forms, and molecular weights. They are designed for wastewater treatment, specifically sludge dewatering/thickening, floatation, clarification, decantation, and coagulation.</p>
